6) Current mmap Lab Program
---------------------------
File:
- src/labs/mmap/map.c

Modes:
- ./bin/program anon
- ./bin/program buf
- ./bin/program file
- ./bin/program all   (default)

Cases:
- case 1 (anon):
  anonymous page mapping + write + munmap

- case 2 (buf):
  anonymous int buffer mapping + fill squares + print + munmap

- case 3 (file):
  file-backed mapping on obj/map.bin + write via mem + msync + readback

Reliability details:
- Handles partial writes with writeall()
- Uses negative errno returns from helpers
- Uses cleanup-oriented control flow for mapping/file resources


